<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .receipt-details {
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .receipt-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Receipt</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Dear {{studentName}},</p>
            
            <p>Your payment has been successfully processed. Please find your receipt details below:</p>
            
            <div class="receipt-details">
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <strong>Receipt Number:</strong>
                    <span>{{receiptNo}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <strong>Fee Type:</strong>
                    <span>{{feeType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <strong>Amount:</strong>
                    <span>₦{{amountNaira}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <strong>Reference:</strong>
                    <span>{{reference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="receipt-row">
                    <strong>Date:</strong>
                    <span>{{date}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Keep this receipt for your records. If you have any questions regarding this payment, please contact the Bursary Office.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your payment.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            COELS Bursary Office</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 COELS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
